&lt;h1 id="write-simply"&gt;Write Simply&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;March 2021&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I try to write using ordinary words and simple sentences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That kind of writing is easier to read, and the easier something is to read, the more deeply readers will engage with it. The less energy they expend on your prose, the more they&amp;rsquo;ll have left for your ideas.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>